description: The demolition of Antony House, Barlborough Street and Edward Robinson House, Reaston Street SE14 and the construction of part three/part four storey blocks, incorporating balconies/terraces, comprising 28x1 bedroom and 28x2 bedroom self-contained flats and part two/part three storey terrace, of 9x3 bedroom and 2x4 bedroom houses, together with associated landscaping, the provision of cycle stores and 40 car parking spaces.
